            <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/1.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px&#34; title=&#34;1&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;1&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/1_thumb.jpg&#34; width=&#34;604&#34; height=&#34;394&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/2.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px&#34; title=&#34;2&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;2&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/2_thumb.jpg&#34; width=&#34;604&#34; height=&#34;482&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/3.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px&#34; title=&#34;3&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;3&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/3_thumb.jpg&#34; width=&#34;604&#34; height=&#34;404&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/4.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px&#34; title=&#34;4&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;4&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/4_thumb.jpg&#34; width=&#34;604&#34; height=&#34;442&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px&#34; title=&#34;5&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;5&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/5_thumb.jpg&#34; width=&#34;304&#34; height=&#34;404&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;昨晚，2010年11月13日晚，14日凌晨。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;狗洞着了。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;一场大火，烧掉了我最爱的新兴，烧掉了广西大学中我最爱的部分。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
        </item><item>
            <title>西大的荷</title>
            <link>https://blognew.natt.cc/posts/2010-07-28-%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%8D%B7/</link>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Jul 2010 01:39:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <guid>https://blognew.natt.cc/posts/2010-07-28-%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E8%8D%B7/</guid>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;大雨冲断了铁路，于是我又留在了广西，背起相机在塘子边上走了走…&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;啥也不多说了，上图吧&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;display: inline; border: 0px;&#34; title=&#34;_MG_2405&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/MG_2405.jpg&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;_MG_2405&#34; width=&#34;360&#34; height=&#34;600&#34; /&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;1.虽然那天太阳不强烈，也是刚下过雨，但在校园走那么大一圈已然是会累死人的&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;display: inline; border: 0px;&#34; title=&#34;_MG_2408&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/MG_2408.jpg&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;_MG_2408&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;360&#34; /&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;2.所谓的纪念碑所在地。 MOMO说如果这片塘子都填上，要盖多少宿舍楼，哪儿还需要住在八人间&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;display: inline; border: 0px;&#34; title=&#34;_MG_2403&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/MG_2403.jpg&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;_MG_2403&#34; width=&#34;360&#34; height=&#34;600&#34; /&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;3.这哥寂寞地站在水中&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;display: inline; border: 0px;&#34; title=&#34;_MG_2398&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/MG_2398.jpg&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;_MG_2398&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;360&#34; /&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;4.每当看到完整的漂浮的荷叶，我就会想起西大东门的荷叶饭&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;display: inline; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; border: 0px;&#34; title=&#34;_MG_2389&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/MG_2389.jpg&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;_MG_2389&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;360&#34; /&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;5.周围都成了莲蓬了，它却依旧是莲花，这就是晚熟的美&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; style=&#34;display: inline; border: 0px;&#34; title=&#34;_MG_2374&#34; src=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/MG_2374.jpg&#34; border=&#34;0&#34; alt=&#34;_MG_2374&#34; width=&#34;600&#34; height=&#34;360&#34; /&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;6.其实，满荷塘荷花不少，但荷叶更多&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;本博客不伺候IE6及IE6-的IE垃圾版本，如果您看到图片扭曲，请更新您那垃圾浏览器&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;推荐：Chrome  Firefox&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
